channel.title: Autospawn question
channel.description:
Can you put //comments in auto spawn to sort it out more?
ex: //Wildy spawn = 86 3232 3533 0 3233 3534 3231 3532 2 Wildy Giant Rat spawn = 87 3237 3529 0 3238 3530 3236 3528 2 Wildy Giant Rat //Falador spawn = 494 3011 3353 0 0........
or will it try and read it and mess up or something?

item.title: Autospawn question
item.dc:creator: @BaracudaX BaracudaX
item.description:
@BaracudaX wrote:

no u can put those and it will not attempt to read them

you should enter a space and skip a line though like this just to make sure

//start of wildy
spawn = 86 3232 3533 0 3233 3534 3231 3532 2 Wildy Giant Rat
spawn = 87 3237 3529 0 3238 3530 3236 3528 2 Wildy Giant Rat

//end of wildy

//start of fally

spawn = 494 3011 3353 0 0…

//end of fally
